{"id":17811,"title":"[A fever of finally known origin].","abstract":"Wir stellen den Fall eines 77-jährigen Mannes vor, bei dem ein unklares Fieber auftrat, das trotz detaillierten Abklärungen zunächst unklar blieb. Erst die Serologie brachte am Schluss die Diagnose eines Q-Fiebers. Retrospektiv passen die Anamnese und die Befunde gut zu einem akuten Q-Fieber.We present the case of a 77 year old man with fever of unknown origin. Despite a thorough assessment in hospital the diagnosis could only be made after discharge when positive results for C. burnetii serology revealed acute Q-fever. However, retrospectively history and clinical findings matched well with acute Q-fever. ","date":"2014-05-21","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24846891","annotations":[{"name":"Fever","weight":0.762559,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fever"},{"name":"Serology","weight":0.746411,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Serology"},{"name":"Medical sign","weight":0.728515,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_sign"},{"name":"Diagnosis","weight":0.723286,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diagnosis"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.476365,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Acute (medicine)","weight":0.402232,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acute_(medicine)"},{"name":"Death","weight":0.029746,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death"},{"name":"Fever of unknown origin","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fever_of_unknown_origin"},{"name":"Clinical psychology","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_psychology"},{"name":"History","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History"},{"name":"Autumn","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Autumn"},{"name":"Discharge (hy